      <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
         <head>Biographical History</head>
         
      <p>Ferran Soldevila (1894-1971) was a Spanish historian, librarian and author.  He taught history at the University of 
	  Catalonia and wrote several important works on Spanish history.</p></bioghist>
      
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
         <p>The <emph render="bold">Ferran Soldevila Papers</emph> consists of manuscripts of Soldevila's work.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      
      <arrangement encodinganalog="351$a">
         <head>Arrangement of the Collection</head>
         <p>The collection consists of five manuscripts which are arranged in alphabetical order by
            title.</p>
      </arrangement>
      
